title: P5 Syndra/Zed Main Youtuber!
body: Hi everyone, I'm Angeline and I'm a starting-out youtuber looking for friends/feedback <3 Hit me up about anything!

replies.body: I find it interesting you max e second on syndra, over w.
For the burst :D You can actually oneshot with Q -> E if you're fed. If I'm not fed I'd take W second for the extra CC.

The general rule is:

* Dont bump more than once every 24 hours.
* Dont bump is no new comments are received. 
* Don't overly bump (i'd say 3 times maximum).

In other words, yes they can! :D
